Hot and Sour Soup:
- Chicken or vegetable broth
- Tofu (cubed)
- Mushrooms (such as shiitake, sliced)
- Bamboo shoots (sliced)
- Eggs (beaten)
- Cornstarch (dissolved in water, for thickening)
- Vinegar (rice vinegar or white vinegar)
- Soy sauce
- Sesame oil
- Red chili flakes or white pepper
- Green onions (chopped)
- Salt and sugar (to taste)
